23class reference_id {
24 int filename_id;
25 int pos;
26public:
27 reference_id() : filename_id(-1) { }
28 reference_id(int fid, int off) : filename_id(fid), pos(off) { }
29 unsigned hash() const { return (filename_id << 4) + pos; }
30 int is_null() const { return filename_id < 0; }
31 friend inline int operator==(const reference_id &, const reference_id &);
32};
33
34inline int operator==(const reference_id &r1, const reference_id &r2)
35{
36 return r1.filename_id == r2.filename_id && r1.pos == r2.pos;
37}
